Modifications by GSplat Realestate add:
- S3-backed QC workflow: load from a signed S3 GET URL (via the upstream
  `?load=` URL param), save cleaned splat to a signed S3 PUT URL minted by our
  Platform Services API.
- Property metadata read from URL params (`?scene_id=<id>&token=<id-token>`).
- QC-only UI mode (toggled by `?qc=1`) that hides non-essential editor panels.

All upstream copyrights and license notices are preserved.
